<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">In Pionex P2P system, users can buy and sell crypto directly with one another using local payment methods. This is mostly used in regions where there are banking restrictions on crypto purchases. By connecting users peer-to-peer, the platform offers easier fiat onboarding and more personalized transaction arrangements.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Although P2P isn’t a primary focus for Pionex, it still acts as an alternative route for deposits and withdrawals when needed. The system has escrow protection, so users&#8217; funds are kept safe until both parties transact successfully. The availability of this feature varies by region, and traders who utilize P2P for a majority of their trades may find more advanced offerings on bigger exchanges.</span></p>
