<p><span data-color="var(--green-10)">No, you do not need a </span><strong><span data-color="var(--green-10)">Coinbase account</span></strong><span data-color="var(--green-10)"> to participate in staking. While Coinbase does offer staking services, you can stake your assets on many other platforms like Binance, Kraken, or decentralized wallets without ever signing up for Coinbase.</span></p>
